    <h1 class="display-3" style="background-color: white; color: black;">
      Resources
    </h1>
    <p class="lead">Government Provided Channels for help:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Helpline Number :<strong>+91-11-23978046</strong></li>
      <li>Toll Free : <strong>1075</strong></li>
      <li>Helpline Email ID : <strong>ncov2019@gov.in</strong></li>
    </ol>
    <a
      href="https://www.mohfw.gov.in/pdf/coronvavirushelplinenumber.pdf"
      class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
      target="_blank"
      >States & U.T. Helpline Numbers</a
