          <h4 class="card-title">MOHFW</h4>
          <p class="card-text">Official site provided by GOI.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a
            href="https://www.mohfw.gov.in/"
            class="btn btn-primary"
            target="_blank"
            >Find Out More!</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <img class="card-img-top" src="images/covid19india-r.jpg" alt="" />
        <div class="card-body">
          <h4 class="card-title">COVID-19 TRACKER India</h4>
          <p class="card-text">
            Due to there crowdsourced patient database, live updates of numbers
            of daily cases, overall cases and others, this site was possible.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a
            href="https://www.covid19india.org/"
            class="btn btn-primary"
            target="_blank"
            >Find Out More!</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
