          <p class="card-text">
            To combat this challenge COVID-19 presents we need to stay united
            regardless of our nationality or religion. WHO's instructions helped
            shaped our motto for this project.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a
            href="https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019"
            class="btn btn-primary"
            target="_blank"
            >Find Out More!</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <img class="card-img-top" src="images/mapmyindia-r.jpg.png" alt="" />
        <div class="card-body">
          <h4 class="card-title">Map My India</h4>
          <p class="card-text">
            Live look of coronavirus impact with numbers in different states.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a
            href="https://www.mapmyindia.com/api/corona/"
            class="btn btn-primary"
            target="_blank"
            >Find Out More!</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
